      "text": "已在 `/tmp/disaster_recovery` 下创建 `scrubbing_tools.py`，核心逻辑如下：\n\n```python\nimport zlib\n\n\ndef apply_hardware_scrubbing(data: bytes) -> bytes:\n    \"\"\"Apply per-byte 0x42 XOR to remove the hardware XOR mask.\n\n    Args:\n        data: Raw bytes as extracted from the crash segment.\n\n    Returns:\n        Bytes with the hardware XOR mask removed.\n    \"\"\"\n    if not isinstance(data, (bytes, bytearray)):\n        raise TypeError(\"data must be bytes or bytearray\")\n\n    mask = 0x42\n    return bytes(b ^ mask for b in data)\n\n\ndef expand_memory_structure(data: bytes) -> bytes:\n    \"\"\"Decompress scrubbed memory data using zlib.\n\n    Args:\n        data: XOR-scrubbed bytes that represent a compressed memory page.\n\n    Returns:\n        Decompressed bytes of the original memory structure.\n\n    Raises:\n        zlib.error: If the data is not valid zlib-compressed content.\n    \"\"\"\n    if not isinstance(data, (bytes, bytearray)):\n        raise TypeError(\"data must be bytes or bytearray\")\n\n    return zlib.decompress(data)\n```\n\n如果你愿意，下一步我可以写一个小的驱动脚本，例如：\n\n1. 从 `crash_segment.bin` 读取十六进制字符串并转换为字节流  \n2. 调用 `apply_hardware_scrubbing`  \n3. 调用 `expand_memory_structure`  \n4. 将解压后的内存页写到 `restored_page.bin`，方便后续结构分析。",
